properties.name: Tangents
properties.description:
Coming up with a route is easy; a reason, less so. We do our best, though. It may be true that these announcements are sometimes only tangentially related to the ride itself, but as long as the tangent is an interesting one, it was not a wasted effort. And, hey, perhaps that's not such a bad description of the ride itself? Sometimes we are able to get right to the heart of the matter, but if not, let us at least hope for a few interesting tangents along the way. Yes, admittedly, we've got a case of writer's block this week, but if you find yourself with a case of rider's block, well, we hope this will shake you out of it.
